ðŸ“ˆ Sample Output
python
Copy
Edit
import pandas as pd

data = pd.Series([10, 20, 30, 40], index=['a', 'b', 'c', 'd'])
print(data)

# Output:
# a    10
# b    20
# c    30
# d    40
# dtype: int64
